 <span data-ttu-id="2e99a-103">实例<xref:Microsoft.SqlServer.Server.SqlTriggerContext>从可用<xref:Microsoft.SqlServer.Server.SqlContext>类，通过触发器内部运行代码时<xref:Microsoft.SqlServer.Server.SqlContext.TriggerContext%2A>属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2e99a-103">An instance of <xref:Microsoft.SqlServer.Server.SqlTriggerContext> is available from the <xref:Microsoft.SqlServer.Server.SqlContext> class, when the code is running inside a trigger through the <xref:Microsoft.SqlServer.Server.SqlContext.TriggerContext%2A> property.</span></span>  
  
   
  
